    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信贷市场因贸易战而瘫痪，将债务交易置于冰上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-junk-credit-markets-plunge-further-on-tariff-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球市场的越来越多的恐惧，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）不断升级的贸易战争引发了全球衰退，公司的债务销售越来越停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-junk-credit-markets-plunge-further-on-tariff-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 11:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自2020年3月以来，债券市场湍流最多可提高30年的收益率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/traders-boost-fed-bets-see-five-more-interest-rate-cuts-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府的债券周一倒闭，消除了自八月以来每周最大进展的一部分，这在迹象表明投资者暂时重新获得了对风险的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/traders-boost-fed-bets-see-five-more-interest-rate-cuts-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 07:11:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券产量的激增，股票震惊的股票：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波动性的浪潮重新震撼了市场，股票，债券和商品被唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战争的另一个头条新闻鞭打，这只会加强在投资和经济方面的云层。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易商提高关税头条的第三届会议的黄金下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/gold-falls-further-at-open-as-traders-assess-tariff-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在四年多的时间里，黄金在三天的撞车事故中处于正轨状态，因为交易者对与唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税政策有关的许多头条新闻反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/gold-falls-further-at-open-as-traders-assess-tariff-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街是特朗普贸易战的附带损害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-tariff-chart-how-stock-market-crash-hits-wall-street-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国投资者班级＆Mdash; 拥有几乎所有股票的前10％; 在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易攻势时代，很快就会遵守其新的，艰巨的地位。从企业高管将其股票期权计算到亿万富翁对冲基金大亨以及介于两者之间的每个人，现在只是附带损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-tariff-chart-how-stock-market-crash-hits-wall-street-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
